176static unsigned int
177joining_type (hb_codepoint_t u)
178{
179 switch (u >> 12)
180 {
181 case 0x0u:
182 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x0600u, hi: 0x08E2u)) return joining_table[u - 0x0600u + joining_offset_0x0600u];
183 break;
184
185 case 0x1u:
186 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x1806u, hi: 0x18AAu)) return joining_table[u - 0x1806u + joining_offset_0x1806u];
187 break;
188
189 case 0x2u:
190 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x200Cu, hi: 0x2069u)) return joining_table[u - 0x200Cu + joining_offset_0x200cu];
191 break;
192
193 case 0xAu:
194 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0xA840u, hi: 0xA873u)) return joining_table[u - 0xA840u + joining_offset_0xa840u];
195 break;
196
197 case 0x10u:
198 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x10AC0u, hi: 0x10AEFu)) return joining_table[u - 0x10AC0u + joining_offset_0x10ac0u];
199 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x10B80u, hi: 0x10BAFu)) return joining_table[u - 0x10B80u + joining_offset_0x10b80u];
200 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x10D00u, hi: 0x10D23u)) return joining_table[u - 0x10D00u + joining_offset_0x10d00u];
201 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x10F30u, hi: 0x10FCBu)) return joining_table[u - 0x10F30u + joining_offset_0x10f30u];
202 break;
203
204 case 0x11u:
205 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x110BDu, hi: 0x110CDu)) return joining_table[u - 0x110BDu + joining_offset_0x110bdu];
206 break;
207
208 case 0x1Eu:
209 if (hb_in_range<hb_codepoint_t> (u, lo: 0x1E900u, hi: 0x1E94Bu)) return joining_table[u - 0x1E900u + joining_offset_0x1e900u];
210 break;
211
212 default:
213 break;
214 }
